  "about": {
    "heroTitle": "Know what your market actually charges",
    "heroLead": "BazarDhor shows you community-submitted prices from local markets in your zone — so you can plan the trip, compare options, and shop with real numbers instead of guesses.",
    "ctaExplore": "Explore markets",
    "ctaCompare": "Compare two markets",
    "whyTitle": "Why we built this",
    "whyParagraph1": "Prices at local markets shift constantly and rarely show up online. The same item can swing 20–30% between two shops a few minutes apart, and the only way to know is to walk in and ask.",
    "whyParagraph2": "BazarDhor turns that legwork into something the community shares. Shoppers submit what they paid, our team verifies it, and the next person looking for the same item gets a real price instead of a guess.",
    "featuresTitle": "What you can do here",
    "feature1Title": "Discover local markets",
    "feature1Desc": "Browse markets in your zone, filter by category, and see ratings, opening hours, and what each market is known for.",
    "feature2Title": "Community-submitted prices",
    "feature2Desc": "See what items actually cost — submitted by people who shopped there, not scraped from generic listings.",
    "feature3Title": "Compare two markets",
    "feature3Desc": "Put any two markets side by side to weigh distance, services, product range, and prices before you head out.",
    "feature4Title": "Verified before published",
    "feature4Desc": "Every price submission goes through admin review, so the data you read is moderated rather than raw user input.",
    "howTitle": "How it works",
    "how1Title": "Pick your zone",
    "how1Desc": "On your first visit we detect your area automatically — every market, price, and search result is scoped to that zone.",
    "how2Title": "Browse and search",
    "how2Desc": "Look up markets by category or search by item. Each listing shows community-submitted prices for what it carries.",
    "how3Title": "Submit what you find",
    "how3Desc": "Spotted a price we don't have? Add it through the in-app form with a photo as proof — it joins the moderation queue.",
    "how4Title": "We verify, you benefit",
    "how4Desc": "Admins review submissions and publish the verified ones, so the next person checking the app gets accurate info.",
    "ctaTitle": "Start with the markets near you",
